EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This project is created for educational and learning purposes only. It is 
inspired by hospital management systems but is NOT intended for production 
use in healthcare settings without proper regulatory compliance, security 
audits, and legal review.

Do not use this software to handle real patient data (PHI/PII) without:
- Proper HIPAA compliance (US)
- GDPR compliance (EU)
- Local healthcare data protection regulations
- Professional security audit
- Legal consultation

The creators and contributors assume no liability for any misuse of this 
software in production healthcare environments.
